# Banner Generator

## When to use

- Generating a project banner image (PNG) for GitHub or documentation
- Auto-detecting project type (CLI, starter kit, Laravel/Filament package)
- Creating banners from composer.json metadata
- Saving banner to `art/{owner}-{repo}.png`

## Keywords

`banner`, `banner generate`, `project banner`, `banners-cli`, `art image`, `github banner`, `banner png`
